title: Nothing Seems Certain...but we're still certain about THIS
itunes:title: Nothing Seems Certain...but we're still certain about THIS
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal break down all the news heading into week 16 including Nick Foles being named Philly's starter again this week (06:41), Cam Newton's status this season (10:30) and Frank Gore's foot injury this season (14:38). Don't miss Pro Bowl snubs (20:48), Nothing seems certain anymore, (26:27) and iTunes reviews (43:46).
